Package: ConvQcENANDES
Title: Conventional Quality Control Tools for ENANDES Project
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Bruce Anthony", family = "Tumbaco Vega",
           email = "bruce.tumbaco@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3558-2923"))
Description: Tools for conventional quality control of daily meteorological
    series used in the ENANDES+ project. Includes format validation,
    logical ranges, Z-score (modified for precipitation; standard for temperatures),
    Isolation Forest, PCA (Mahalanobis distance), Autoencoder (H2O),
    visualization and export helpers.
